summary:
Avengers: Endgame (No Spoilers)
I’ve been waiting for Endgame since Infinity war came out and now that I’m seeing it soon I’m...
body:
Avengers: Endgame (No Spoilers)

I’ve been waiting for Endgame since Infinity war came out and now that I’m seeing it soon I’m getting really anxious for it? I don’t know how to prepare myself for it because of the things I’ve heard about it. (Mainly people fainting during the test screening.

I know pretty much the whole Marvel fanbase is freaking out right now but I’m just wondering is there a way to mentally prepare myself for Endgame???

caption:
Hi guys!… Let’s play a game 😎
I’m Italian and in Italy the football is the most popular sport.
We all create the #AVENGERS FOOTBALL CLUB team ok?
I started it, inserting the goalkeeper: #CaptainAmerica
Ok, it’s now your turn… Write 4 names characters ( #marvel ) to be inserted as Defenders. I’ll insert in the TEAM the most voted in two days, ok?
START WRITING! 😉
.
Ciao ragazzi!… Facciamo un gioco 😎
Creiamo insieme il team AVENGERS FOOTBALL CLUB?
Ho iniziato io inserendo il portiere: Captain America
Ok ora è il vostro turno… Scrivete 4 nomi di personaggi Marvel da inserire come difensori. Inserirò nel TEAM i più votati tra 2 giorni, ok?
INIZIATE A SCRIVERE! 😉
.

summary: It sucks you in and kicks you down And chews you up and spits you out It messes with your sanity by twisting all your thoughts...
caption:
It sucks you in and kicks you down
And chews you up and spits you out
It messes with your sanity by twisting all your thoughts around
They say it’s blind, they say it waits
But every time it seals your fate
Now it’s got you by the balls and won’t let go until you fall
I was down and out, got up, and said
“Hey love, I’ve had enough!”
I’ve felt pleasure without pain
My soul you’ll never tame

summary: The Ultimate Marvel Mashup 4/7: Delete that footage! Watch the full series:  Part 1 – Part 2 – Part 3 – Part 5 – Part 6 – Part 7...
caption:
The Ultimate Marvel Mashup 4/7: Delete that footage!

Watch the full series:  Part 1 – Part 2 – Part 3 – Part 5 – Part 6 – Part 7

The musical mashup is the genius work of Ben Kling (in fact, the series represents a good chunk of his mashup album Double Dutch: Part II, which is itself a compilation of over a hundred artists.) The footage is all, of course, the property of Disney/Marvel, and is the result of the hard work of thousands.

I just put them both together, which often felt like building a mediocre sandcastle in front of the Taj Majal.
